long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Embark on a spine-tingling adventure into the surreal world of the Backrooms Game. Trapped in an endless labyrinth of eerily mundane rooms, you must navigate through the darkness, evade lurking threats, and uncover the secrets that lie within. With each step, the tension mounts, and every corner holds new horrors to encounter. Will you find your way out, or become lost in the haunting depths of the Backrooms forever?
